node.text: The Southwest’s starkly stunning landscape inspired the most distinctive aspect of the style: the palette. Browns, rusts, ambers, and tans dominate, but they’re complemented by the pale pinks of sunrises over the mesas and the fiery reds of sunsets over the mountains. 🌅 Tap to shop and head to the link in our bio to get the look.
